To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private HikkakeModified _hikkakemodified;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_hikkakemodified = HikkakeModified(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_hikkakemodified.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "HikkakeModified Period", _hikkakemodified.Period);
    Plot("My Indicators", "HikkakeModified Current", _hikkakemodified.Current);
}
# In Initialize()
symbol = self.AddEquity("SPY").Symbol
self.hikkakemodified = self.HikkakeModified(symbol)

# In OnData()
if self.hikkakemodified.IsReady:
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "HikkakeModified Period", self.hikkakemodified.Period)
    self.Plot("My Indicators", "HikkakeModified Current", self.hikkakemodified.Current)

For more information about plotting indicators, see Plotting Indicators.
